title: MQM delegation calls on prime minister
content:
KARACHI, Jul 26 (APP): A delegation of the Muttahida Qaumi Movement (MQM) headed by Convenor Khalid Maqbool Siddiqui on Wednesday called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here.
The delegation comprised Sindh Governor Kamran Tessori, Dr Farooq Sattar and Mustafa Kamal.
In the meeting, they discussed the overall political situation in the country.
